  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators collect nasopharyngeal epithelium samples from healthy individuals and
      analyze for biomarkers compared with tumor tissues from another clinical research project.
      The goal of this study is to identify molecular biomarkers for prediction of nasopharyngeal
      carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
